headline.main: E.U. Lawmakers Call for End to Visa-Free Travel for Americans
headline.print_headline: Europeans Vote to Alter Visa Rules of Americans

lead_paragraph: The spokesman for the Libyan coast guard says 115 migrants have been rescued off of Libyan shores, and 25 others have gone missing as they attempted to cross the Mediterranean.
